FBIS4-60222 "drnes099_j_94050" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 22 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Al-'Attas To Form National Unity Government Al-'Attas To Form National Unity Government EA2205190594 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 22 May 94 EA2205190594 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] Brother Dr. 'Ali Salim al-Bid, chairman of the Presidential Council, today issued Presidential Council Decree no. 3 of 1994. The first article charges brother engineer Haydar Abu-Bakr al-'Attas to form a government of national unity in consultation with the Presidential Council. The other articles provide for the implementation of the decree with effect from the date of its issuance, and for its publication in the official gazette.
